            "id": 6011091,
            "title": "川、習熱線通話90分鐘 總統府：樂見穩定區域情勢",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國總統川普本周四 (5 日) 在社群平台上發文指出，他已與中國國家主席習近平進行了一通約 90 分鐘的電話會談，雙方討論了最近達成的貿易協議細節，並同意盡速安排新一輪會談。總統府發言人郭雅慧今 (6) 日表示，我國一向支持並樂見任何有助於穩定區域，台灣將持續與美方緊密聯繫，共同致力於區域的和平與繁榮發展。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011091%2Fl%2F7a17644447e092b3904ecee934956fd4.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">川、習熱線通話90分鐘，總統府：樂見穩定區域情勢。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>據川普形容，這次對話「結果對兩國都非常正面」，同時也解決了稀土產品的複雜性問題。習近平也邀請他訪問中國，他也請習赴美，雙方都接受邀請。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普表示，美方未來將派出財政部長貝森特等官員及美國貿易代表參加中美新一輪會談，日後將公布舉行會議及時間，並強調通話「幾乎完全聚焦在貿易問題」，並未涉及俄羅斯、烏克蘭或伊朗事務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>對中、美雙方最高元首通話一事，郭雅惠表示，已注意到川普總統就美中貿易及芬太尼毒品等議題與中方進行討論。對美中領袖對話，我國一向支持並樂見任何有助於穩定區域情勢，遏制威權擴張風險的努力，台灣將持續與美方緊密聯繫，共同致力於區域的和平與繁榮發展。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
